title: Colin Cowherd Podcast - Prime Cuts: Peyton and Eli Manning, Nick Wright, Joel Klatt on Chip Kelly's UCLA rebuild
itunes:title: Colin Cowherd Podcast - Prime Cuts: Peyton and Eli Manning, Nick Wright, Joel Klatt on Chip Kelly's UCLA rebuild
description:
The best of The Colin Cowherd Podcast. Peyton and Eli Manning on their new show, "Monday Night Football with Peyton and Eli" and some hilarious stories from their playing days (1:45). Nick Wright on the psychology behind Aaron Rodgers' issues and the one thing the Packers QB can't publicly admit (20:20). FOX College Football Analyst Joel Klatt on what Chip Kelly and UCLA are doing as well as any program in the country (35:03). Make sure to follow Colin and The Volume on Twitter, Instagram and YouTube for the latest content and updates, and check out FanDuel for the best wagering and daily fantasy action!
